quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Dájúdájú àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo ti jèrè
  23,2,Àwọn t’ó ń páyà (Allāhu) nínú ìrun wọn
  23,3,àti àwọn t’ó ń ṣẹ́rí kúrò níbi ìsọkúsọ
  23,4,àti àwọn t’ó ń yọ Zakāh
  23,5,àti àwọn t’ó ń ṣọ́ abẹ́ wọn
  23,6,àfi ní ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn ìyàwó wọn àti ẹrúbìnrin wọn. Dájúdájú wọn kì í ṣe ẹni èébú (tí wọ́n bá súnmọ́ wọn)
  23,7,"nítorí náà, ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá wá òmíràn (súnmọ́) lẹ́yìn ìyẹn, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni àwọn olùtayọ ẹnu-àlà"
  23,8,àti àwọn t’ó ń ṣọ́ àgbàfipamọ́ wọn àti àdéhùn wọn
  23,9,àti àwọn t’ó ń ṣọ́ ìrun wọn
  23,10,àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni àwọn olùjogún
  23,11,àwọn t’ó máa jogún ọgbà ìdẹ̀ra Firdaos. Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀
  23,12,Dájúdájú A ti ṣe ẹ̀dá ènìyàn láti inú ohun tí A mọ jáde láti inú erùpẹ̀ amọ̀
  23,13,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A ṣe é ní àtọ̀ sínú àyè ààbò (ìyẹn, ilé-ọmọ)"
  23,14,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A sọ àtọ̀ di ẹ̀jẹ̀ dídì. Lẹ́yìn náà, A sọ ẹ̀jẹ̀ dídì di bááṣí ẹran. Lẹ́yìn náà, A sọ bááṣí ẹran di eegun. Lẹ́yìn náà, A fi ẹran bo eegun. Lẹ́yìn náà, A sọ ọ́ di ẹ̀dá mìíràn.1 Nítorí náà, ìbùkún ni fún Allāhu, Ẹni t’Ó dára jùlọ nínú àwọn ẹlẹ́dàá (oníṣẹ́-ọnà)"
  23,15,"Lẹ́yìn náà, lẹ́yìn ìyẹn, dájúdájú ẹ̀yin yó sì di òkú"
  23,16,"Lẹ́yìn náà, dájúdájú ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde Wọ́n máa gbe yín dìde"
  23,17,Dájúdájú A dá àwọn sánmọ̀ méje sí òkè yín. Àwa kò sì níí dágunlá sí àwọn ẹ̀dá
  23,18,"À ń sọ omi kalẹ̀ láti sánmọ̀ níwọ̀n níwọ̀n. Lẹ́yìn náà, À ń mú un dúró sínú ilẹ̀. Dájúdájú Àwa kúkú lágbára láti mú un lọ"
  23,19,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A dá àwọn ọgbà oko dàbínù àti àjàrà fun yín; ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ èso wà nínú rẹ̀ fun yín, ẹ sì ń jẹ nínú rẹ̀"
  23,20,Àti igi kan t’ó ń hù jáde níbi àpáta Sīnā’; ó ń mú epo àti n̄ǹkan ìṣebẹ̀ jáde fún àwọn t’ó ń jẹ ẹ́
  23,21,"Àti pé dájúdájú àríwòye wà fun yín lára àwọn ẹran-ọ̀sìn; À ń fun yín mu nínú ohun tí ó wà nínú ikùn wọn. Àwọn àǹfààní ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ (mìíràn) tún wà fun yín lára wọn, ẹ sì ń jẹ nínú rẹ̀"
  23,22,Ẹ sì ń kó ẹrù sí orí àwọn ẹran ọ̀sìn àti ọkọ̀ ojú-omi
  23,23,"Dájúdájú A rán (Ànábì) Nūh níṣẹ́ sí ìjọ rẹ̀. Ó sì sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjọ mi, ẹ jọ́sìn fún Allāhu. Ẹ ò ní ọlọ́hun mìíràn lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀. Ṣé ẹ ò níí bẹ̀rù (Rẹ̀) ni?”"
  23,24,"Àwọn olórí tí wọ́n ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ sọ pé: “Kí ni èyí bí kò ṣe abara kan bí irú yín, tí ó fẹ́ gbé àjùlọ fún ara rẹ̀ lórí yín. Àti pé tí ó bá jẹ́ pé Allāhu bá fẹ́ (ránṣẹ́ sí wa ni), ìbá sọ mọlāika kan kalẹ̀ ni. A kò sì gbọ́ èyí rí lọ́dọ̀ àwọn bàbá wa, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́"
  23,25,"Kò jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe ọkùnrin kan tí àlùjànnú ń bẹ lára rẹ̀. Nítorí náà, ẹ máa retí (ìkángun) rẹ̀ títí di ìgbà kan ná.”"
  23,26,"(Ànábì) Nūh sọ pé: \"Olúwa mi, ṣàrànṣe fún mi nítorí pé wọ́n pè mí ní òpùrọ́"
  23,27,"Nítorí náà, A fi ìmísí ránṣẹ́ sí i pé: \"Ṣe ọkọ̀ ojú-omi ní ojú Wa (báyìí) pẹ̀lú ìmísí Wa. Nígbà tí àṣẹ Wa bá dé, tí omi bá ṣẹ́ yọ ní ojú àrò, nígbà náà ni kí o kó sínú ọkọ̀ ojú-omi gbogbo n̄ǹkan ní oríṣi méjì takọ-tabo àti ará ilé rẹ, àyàfi ẹni tí ọ̀rọ̀ náà kò lé lórí nínú wọn (fún ìparun). Má ṣe bá Mi sọ̀rọ̀ nípa àwọn t’ó ṣàbòsí; dájúdájú A óò tẹ̀ wọ́n rì sínú omi ni"
  23,28,"Nígbà tí o bá jókòó sínú ọkọ̀ ojú-omi náà, ìwọ àti àwọn t’ó wà pẹ̀lú rẹ, sọ pé: 'Ọpẹ́ ni fún Allāhu, Ẹni tí Ó gbà wá là lọ́wọ́ ijọ alábòsí"
  23,29,"Sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, sọ̀ mí kalẹ̀ sí ibùsọ̀ ìbùkún. Ìwọ sì lóore jùlọ nínú àwọn amúnigúnlẹ̀.”"
  23,30,Dájúdájú àwọn àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Àwa sì ni À ń dán ẹ̀dá wò
  23,31,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A mú àwọn ìran mìíràn wá lẹ́yìn wọn"
  23,32,"A tún rán Òjíṣẹ́ kan sí wọn láààrin ara wọn (láti jíṣẹ́) pé: “Ẹ jọ́sìn fún Allāhu. Ẹ ò ní ọlọ́hun mìíràn lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀. Nítorí náà, ṣé ẹ ò níí bẹ̀rù (Rẹ̀) ni?”"
  23,33,"Àwọn olórí t’ó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú ìjọ rẹ̀, àwọn t’ó pe ìpàdé Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn nírọ́, àwọn tí A ṣe gbẹdẹmukẹ fún nínú ìṣẹ̀mí ayé yìí, wọ́n wí pé: \"Kí ni èyí bí kò ṣe abara kan bí irú yín; ó ń jẹ nínú ohun tí ẹ̀ ń jẹ, ó sì ń mu nínú ohun tí ẹ̀ ń mu"
  23,34,"Tí ẹ bá fi lè tẹ̀lé abara kan bí irú yín, dájúdájú ẹ mà ti di ẹni òfò nìyẹn"
  23,35,"Ṣé ó ń ṣe àdéhùn fun yín pé nígbà tí ẹ bá kú, tí ẹ sì di erùpẹ̀ àti egungun tán, dájúdájú Wọn yóò mu yín jáde (ní alààyè)"